User groups and roles.

Visitor.

	Yes:
		Can view site.
		Change query paramaters and see results

	No:
		Does not have access to maintenace section
		Does not have access to managers pages
		Can not edit any records.


Employee.
	
	Yes:
		Can view site.
		Has access to maintenance section
		Change query parameters and see results
		Can add new movies/seansees and other business information


	No:
		Can not edit existing employee list
		Acessing managers pages. (employee lists, CRUDS)

Manager.

	Yes:
		Do anything he wants